Package: moneca
Title: Mobility Network Clustering Analysis
Description: Creates weighted networks from mobility tables and uses cliques to
    identify discrete and nested clusters of positions with high internal mobility.
    Includes modern ggraph visualizations, synthetic data generation for testing,
    and quality metrics for assessing segmentation performance. Maintained fork
    of the original MONECA package with streamlined API and enhanced documentation.
URL: https://gmontaletti.github.io/MONECA/,
        https://github.com/gmontaletti/MONECA
Version: 1.0.0
Maintainer: Giampaolo Montaletti <giampaolo.montaletti@gmail.com>
